statements: SELECT * FROM Partnerships;
SELECT NGO_name, business_name, partnership_type FROM Partnerships WHERE partnership_status = 'Active';
SELECT business_name, partnership_start_date FROM Partnerships WHERE partnership_type = 'Sponsorship';
SELECT partnership_end_date, partnership_status FROM Partnerships ORDER BY partnership_start_date DESC;
SELECT partnership_id, NGO_name, business_name FROM Partnerships WHERE partnership_id IN (1, 3, 5);
SELECT * FROM Partnerships WHERE partnership_status = 'Active' ORDER BY partnership_start_date DESC, NGO_name ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT partnership_id, NGO_name, business_name FROM Partnerships WHERE partnership_type = 'Sponsorship' ORDER BY partnership_end_date ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT DISTINCT business_name FROM Partnerships WHERE partnership_status IN ('Inactive', 'Expired') ORDER BY business_name ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT partnership_status, COUNT(*) AS partnership_count FROM Partnerships GROUP BY partnership_status HAVING partnership_count > 1 ORDER BY partnership_count DESC;
SELECT * FROM Partnerships WHERE partnership_start_date BETWEEN '2023-01-01' AND '2023-12-31' AND partnership_status = 'Active' ORDER BY partnership_start_date ASC LIMIT 5;
